### Test Buddy AI API Endpoints

### 1. Test Chat Streaming
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello Buddy! Can you help me with a task?",
  "sessionId": "test-session-1"
}

### 2. Test Tools Specification
GET http://localhost:8083/api/tools/spec

### 3. Test Notes Tool - Save Note
POST http://localhost:8083/api/tools/execute/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "save: Meeting Notes Important discussion about project timeline"
}

### 4. Test Notes Tool - List Notes
POST http://localhost:8083/api/tools/execute/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "list"
}

### 5. Test Notes Tool - Get Note
POST http://localhost:8083/api/tools/execute/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "get: Meeting Notes"
}

### 6. Test Web Search Tool
